This 2-page, foldout guide discusses the importance of managing stress and maintaining health with essential oils, along with keeping your spine in alignment with chiropractic. It shares the oils and blends that help with 29 common conditions associated with long-term stress. It also includes a worksheet for identifying physical, emotional, and chemical stressors to be addressed with the tandem treatments. Dimensions: 8½" wide x 11" tall; 17" wide unfolded.
